        <STIG_DATA>
          <VULN_ATTRIBUTE>Vuln_Discuss</VULN_ATTRIBUTE>
          <ATTRIBUTE_DATA>An attacker might compromise a VM by making use the dvFilter API. Configure only those VMs to use the API that need this access.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
